		<credit project="CfPBoK@https://slebok.github.io/cfpbok/"/>
		<h1>Topic <code>T2A</code>: Lifecycle</h1>
		Lifecycle + Legacy + Retirement. Work that foregrounds end-to-end language governance: adoption, rollout, operations, deprecation, retirement, legacy language handling, organisational or process aspects of sustaining languages. If the technical core is in changing or maintaining the language, we lean towards using <a href="t2b.html">T2B</a>.
